description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20 Minute Everyday Yoga Flow | Daily Routine To Feel Your Best' from the channel Charlie Follows.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Nature Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Welcome to your 20 min everyday yoga flow. This class is great for all levels and includes a full body routine that you can do daily to feel your best.

This yoga flow includes options to suit all levels and is intended to give you a well rounded practice that you can come back to every day.

The sequence includes a steady vinyasa flow with hip openers, backbends, standing balances and twists. It's designed to help you feel like you've given your body everything it needs to have a great day. 

I hope you enjoy this everyday yoga flow. 

Charlie x
